"<strong>You have an alternative to breaking this law,</strong> or feeling "
"very restrained when you abide to it. GNU/Linux is <a href=\"https://www."
"softwareliberty.com/\" rel=\"external\">Free Software</a> (much better than "
"just freeware): its <a href=\"https://www.gnu.org/copyleft/gpl.html\" rel="
